    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is very reliable; the engine starts up immediately and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. The interior is clean and comfortable, though you will find some light wear on the driver's seat and a few minor scuffs on the plastic trim. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice gloss, but there are a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scratch on the rear bumper consistent with normal use. Overall, it is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing any immediate repairs.",
