    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have taken such good care of it, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new but without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
