    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly investment-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, and the original 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records documenting every scheduled maintenance performed by certified technicians. With no leaks, no modifications, and a smooth, powerful performance, this vehicle is the pinnacle of its class and ready for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
